# Implementation Plan - Alias Package Suggestions

The user wants the "Aliases" input in the Alias Form to provide dropdown suggestions from the database, similar to the Vulnerability Search.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> We will reuse the existing `/api/v1/vulnerabilities/search` endpoint to find package names. The frontend will extract unique package names from the vulnerability search results to populate the suggestions.

## Proposed Changes

### Frontend Components

#### [NEW] [PackageTagInput.tsx](file:///C:/SCOUTNEW/scout_db/frontend/src/components/shared/PackageTagInput.tsx)
- Create a new component based on [TagInput](file:///C:/SCOUTNEW/scout_db/frontend/src/components/shared/TagInput.tsx#15-98) and [VulnerabilitySearch](file:///C:/SCOUTNEW/scout_db/frontend/src/components/VulnerabilitySearch.tsx#35-236).
- **Features**:
