    - Input field triggers async search to `/api/v1/vulnerabilities/search` on typing.
    - Displays a dropdown of unique *package names* found in the search results.
    - Selecting a suggestion adds it as a tag.
    - Pressing Enter adds the current input as a tag (manual entry).

